  body
    // Header
    section#header
      header
        h1 Galactic
        p Decentralized Smart Payments
      footer
        a.button.style2.scrolly-middle(href='#banner') What is Galactic

    // Banner
    section#banner
      header
        h2 Galactic Network
      p
        | A new economy created by the people for the people.
        br
        | 				We will decentralize everything.
        br
        | 				We are going to use smart contracts to create a meritocratic utopia. Starting with payments
      footer
        a.button.style2.scrolly(href='#benefits') Features

    section#benefits.ni-section.ni-section-dark.section-home-benefits
      .container
        .row(class='150%')
          .6u(class='12u$(medium)')
            header.major
              i.fa.fa-server
              .text
                .key Byzantine Fault-Tolerant
                .value
                  | Galactic Network tolerates up to one third of the network failing arbitrarily. This includes explicitly malicious behavior.
          div(class='6u$ 12u$(medium) important(medium)')
            header.major
              i.fa.fa-clone
              .text
                .key Transaction Replication
                .value
                  | Galactic will replicate your transactions on all nodes running in the Galactic Network.

          .6u(class='12u$(medium)')
            header.major
              i.fa.fa-lock
              .text
                .key Secure P2P
                .value
                  | Gossip protocols and peer discovery are secured via Galactic's cryptographic security system.
          div(class='6u$ 12u$(medium) important(medium)')
            header.major
              i.fa.fa-bolt
              .text
                .key Lightning Fast
                .value Galactic supports thousands of transaction per second at sub 500ms latencies.

           .6u(class='12u$(medium)')
             header.major
               i.fa.fa-cloud-upload
               .text
                 .key Easy to Deploy
                 .value
                   | Packaged to use Heroku or AWS EBS to deploy your app.
           div(class='6u$ 12u$(medium) important(medium)')
             header.major
               i.fa.fa-code
               .text
                 .key 100% Open Source
                 .value
                   | All of Galactic's source code will be available soon
                   // Check it out on
                   //a(href='https://github.com/tendermint') GitHub
                   | .

        footer
          a.button.style2.scrolly-middle(href='#first') Roadmap

    // Feature 1
    article#first.container.box.style1.right
      a.image.fit(href='img/decentralized.jpg')
